1205
01:04:04,267 --> 01:04:06,148
have a working their way around that.

1206
01:04:06,268 --> 01:04:09,230
So I would think that'd be the solution to it.

1207
01:04:09,370 --> 01:04:13,092
So hopefully that's happening.

